scenes.description: Nanashi Mumei and Tokoyami Towa conclude their performance and share a brief farewell.
Instrumental transition to the next performance.
Nanashi Mumei and Inugami Korone perform the song 'Trino City'.
MC section where Mumei and Korone talk about their performance and baseball.
